1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
ظآزLet me write the legendظآز

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 16=

4
00:00:19,199 --> 00:00:22,320
Today, you'll die.

5
00:00:30,239 --> 00:00:32,320
Peng Dasheng, prepare to die!

6
00:00:34,759 --> 00:00:35,840
Tianji Armor!

7
00:00:44,719 --> 00:00:46,039
Buddha's Fury Lotus!

8
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,759
You're Tang Changsheng,

9
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:48,920
an elder of the Tang Clan!

10
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:51,600
Now that you know my name,

11
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,719
kneel and die!

12
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,560
(The Tang Clan's hidden weapons
are second to none.)

13
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:57,960
(Beating him)

14
00:00:58,399 --> 00:00:59,880
(won't be easy.)

15
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:01,240
Gulu.

16
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,240
Let's go!

17
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,320
Gulu!

18
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,879
Don't chase them.
Saving lives comes first. Hurry!

19
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,560
Holy Maiden, you're awake.

20
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,560
Did you find Master's body?

21
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,079
We've prepared his body for burial.

22
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,439
Where's Mu Xiao?

23
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,480
Where is she?

24
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,000
Envoy Mu... she...

25
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:41,159
What happened? Tell me!

26
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:45,040
Holy Maiden, Envoy Mu is back.

27
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,200
She's back?

28
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,000
Xiao!

29
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,799
Xiao!

30
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,799
Xiao!

31
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:00,959
Xiao!

32
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,760
Xiao!

33
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,439
And you are?

34
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,800
Amitabha.

35
00:02:10,719 --> 00:02:13,039
(Master Liaode, Abbot of Shaolin Temple)
I am Liaode.

36
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,879
He's Daoist Qingxu

37
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,000
of the Wudang Sect.

38
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,400
(Daoist Qingxu, Wudang Sect)
of the Wudang Sect.

39
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:21,360
We were on our way to Gusu
with our disciples

40
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:24,759
when we came across this young lady.

41
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,199
Thank you both for saving her.

42
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,639
Think nothing of it.

43
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:44,879
We have other matters to attend to,

44
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,960
so we'll be on our way.

45
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:50,280
Amitabha.

46
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,879
Safe travels.

47
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,759
Take Xiao inside
and treat her wounds. Hurry!

48
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,280
How strange. Very strange.

49
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,520
Wait, Mr. Tang,

50
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:18,240
what's wrong with my friend?

51
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,039
Ever since he swallowed the soul jade,

52
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:24,280
the spiritual power inside him

53
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,840
has been raging like wildfire.

54
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,360
If this were anyone else,

55
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:30,680
their meridians
would be burned beyond repair.

56
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,680
Instead,

57
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,159
his meridians

58
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,879
are still intact

59
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,479
and brimming with energy.

60
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,240
So you're saying he's okay?

61
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,159
No.

62
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,360
Quite the opposite.

63
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,479
His pulse points

64
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:45,080
to only one explanation.

65
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,520
His body is refining

66
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,879
the spiritual power
inside the soul jade.

67
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,879
Once all that power is released,

68
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:53,280
it'll turn against him.

69
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,360
His meridians will rupture,
and he'll die.

70
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,680
I've sealed his vital meridians,

71
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,080
but that will only buy him a few days.

72
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,039
Grandfather,

73
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:03,560
doesn't spiritual power
boost cultivation?

74
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,840
Why is he still in danger?

75
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,400
Yeah, why?

76
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,240
You're right.

77
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,960
It can boost cultivation quickly,

78
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:11,520
but it has to be absorbed

79
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,000
little by little.

80
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:16,000
But he's gaining
the spiritual power far too quickly.

81
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,279
It's like

82
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,560
swallowing food whole

83
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,480
and forcing a plant to grow.

84
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,160
Push anything too far,
and it'll backfire.

85
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:24,519
And he was born with sealed meridians.

86
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,800
That only makes it worse.

87
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,240
Mr. Tang, just tell me.

88
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,879
Can you save him?

89
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:31,560
With my skills,

90
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,360
he's beyond saving.

91
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,800
But if he returns to his sect at once,

92
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,879
his master may still

93
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:39,439
be able to save him.

94
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,279
Otherwise,

95
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:42,279
not even an immortal

96
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:44,279
could save him.

97
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,199
Xiaojiu!

98
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:48,879
Xiaojiu!

99
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,560
Xiaojiu!

100
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,199
Whether he lives or dies

101
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:57,160
is up to him now.

102
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:00,620
(Tomb of the Late Master Wu Yangzi)

103
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,399
Master's spirit

104
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,279
will protect us.

105
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,040
He'll protect us,

106
00:05:12,079 --> 00:05:13,639
but who'll protect him?

107
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,279
The Demon Sect's blood debt

108
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:24,000
must be repaid in blood.

109
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,879
Blood for blood!

110
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:12,170
ظآزOne thought pulls me in, the mortal
world becomes the battlefieldظآز

111
00:06:12,970 --> 00:06:18,030
ظآزWho traded true love
for a body covered in scars?ظآز

112
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:25,770
ظآزThe lanterns still burn,
but the vows have grown coldظآز

113
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:30,000
ظآزThe road behind lies deep in snow,
but can't erase your warmthظآز

114
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,879
Xiaojiu.

115
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,880
ظآزSomeone gave their lifeظآز

116
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,720
Xiaojiu.

117
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:39,160
ظآزTo keep one lantern brightظآز

118
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:45,660
ظآزIt lit the barren road
and showed our last goodbyeظآز

119
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,720
Xiaojiu!

120
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,639
Don't go!

121
00:06:53,130 --> 00:06:57,970
ظآزDon't ask when I'll return,
just what this life was worthظآز

122
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:04,770
ظآزOne vow became a curse,
one dream dissolved from viewظآز

123
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:10,370
ظآزYou gave your whole life
so I'd live without regretظآز

124
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:15,420
ظآزIf in this martial worldظآز
(Yaowang Residence)

125
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:19,330
ظآزOne heart must break in twoظآز

126
00:07:19,470 --> 00:07:25,100
ظآزWhy must every lifetime
lead me back to you?ظآز

127
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,720
Don't leave me.

128
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,519
Xiaojiu.

129
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:34,879
Xiaojiu.

130
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,600
Xiaojiu.

131
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,600
Xiaojiu.

132
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,920
Xiaojiu, don't leave me.

133
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,759
Xiaojiu!

134
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,160
Xiaojiu!

135
00:08:00,220 --> 00:08:06,140
ظآزI hide my whole life
beneath a cold and lonely moonظآز

136
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,160
Xiaojiu.

137
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:11,600
Don't leave me.

138
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,720
Xiaojiu.

139
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,160
Don't leave me.

140
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:22,680
ظآزOne vow became a curse,
one dream dissolved from viewظآز

141
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,839
Xiaojiu.

142
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:30,680
(Maybe you'll never love me.)

143
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:32,679
(But for one moment,)

144
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,960
(I was the one on your mind.)

145
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,480
(Even if I was only her stand-in,)

146
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,919
(that was enough.)

147
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:45,900
ظآزWhy must every lifetime
lead me back to you?ظآز

148
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:50,940
ظآزPetals fall like snow,
while love slips out of reachظآز

149
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,360
My heart already belongs
to someone else.

150
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:59,279
Miss, don't tell me
you've fallen for him.

151
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:00,600
Truth is,

152
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,159
my master told me when I was little

153
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,360
that I was born with sealed meridians

154
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,440
and wasn't meant to live long.

155
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,399
(Peng Dasheng,)

156
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,440
(stay alive.)

157
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,279
(I hope we meet again.)

158
00:09:13,180 --> 00:09:15,780
ظآزBut this life we were givenظآز

159
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:23,900
ظآزCan never be rewrittenظآز

160
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,039
How's Dasheng?

161
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,480
He still hasn't gone back
to Wuhu Mountain?

162
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,519
No.

163
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,919
He's locked himself in his room drinking

164
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:38,720
and won't see anyone.

165
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,120
What do we do?

166
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,399
I'll go see him.

167
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,840
Don't go in yet.

168
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,840
This has hit him hard.

169
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:48,000
Give him some time to sort things out.

170
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,000
You little rascal.

171
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:03,320
Do you remember our one-month agreement?

172
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,759
Master?

173
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:12,759
Master!

174
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,879
So you haven't forgotten me.

175
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,360
Tell me.

176
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:20,480
Do you realize
you only have a few days left?

177
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:22,639
I do, Master.

178
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,679
But I...

179
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:26,200
But you've let love consume you.

180
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:28,200
You've almost forgotten who you are.

181
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,679
Am I right?

182
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,799
Nothing gets past you, Master.

183
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:40,879
You've already used up
every pill I gave you before you left.

184
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:43,360
And your 20th birthday is almost here.

185
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:45,159
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

186
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,399
Master,

187
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,480
I can't go back yet.

188
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:55,360
So please find a way

189
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:57,639
to change my fate and keep me alive.

190
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:03,679
You really think I'm an immortal?

191
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,679
Fate is decreed by heaven.

192
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:07,159
No mortal can change it.

193
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:09,120
All I can do

194
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,519
is buy you more time.

195
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:12,960
Understand?

196
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:16,240
Master,

197
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:18,360
then make me more

198
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,879
of those pills.

199
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,120
Just enough for three to five months.

200
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:28,679
You think the Kunlun snow lotuses
I use to make your pills

201
00:11:28,679 --> 00:11:30,360
grow in our backyard?

202
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,639
It took me three full years

203
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:34,159
to gather enough for those pills.

204
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,919
Three years!

205
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,960
Then, if I go back to the sect,

206
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,200
I won't be able to leave
for another three years?

207
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,480
Of course not.

208
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,759
It's not that you can't leave
for three years.

209
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:49,039
You can never leave again.

210
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,639
Why?

211
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:53,639
Your destined tribulation

212
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:57,080
comes at twenty.

213
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:59,720
If you stay at the sect,

214
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:03,639
I can use everything I know
to keep you safe.

215
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:05,440
But once you leave,

216
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,080
no amount of medicine

217
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,679
can save you.

218
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,519
Master,

219
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,039
what if I don't go back?

220
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:21,600
Heaven's will is ever-changing,

221
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:24,039
and fate is impossible to predict.

222
00:12:24,639 --> 00:12:26,360
All I know is that

223
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,919
after your 20th birthday,

224
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:32,039
any day could be your last.

225
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:41,340
ظآزCome onظآز

226
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:46,540
ظآزThis battle, I won't retreatظآز

227
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:51,460
ظآزIn worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dustظآز

228
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:54,660
ظآزAmong the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?ظآز

229
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:57,740
ظآزThey say my birth
has already decided my pathظآز

230
00:12:58,140 --> 00:13:00,740
ظآزBut I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worthظآز

231
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:04,220
ظآزWith one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless stormsظآز

232
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:07,460
ظآزCovered in scars,
only to be called young and recklessظآز

233
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:10,540
ظآزIf this world only bows
to status and bloodlinesظآز

234
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:13,460
ظآزThen I'll break every rule
with a single slashظآز

235
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:17,340
ظآزListen, this heartbeat echoesظآز

236
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:20,380
ظآزFate is nothing but a netظآز

237
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:26,060
ظآزEither be trapped by it
or tear it apartظآز

238
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:28,500
ظآزI rise against fate and fightظآز

239
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:31,580
ظآزI don't believe
anyone is born above anotherظآز

240
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:34,700
ظآزEven this mortal body
dares to fight backظآز

241
00:13:34,820 --> 00:13:38,500
ظآزI'll step on fate and grow beyond itظآز

242
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:41,220
ظآزI rise against fate and fightظآز

243
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:44,260
ظآزEven if the world's cold stares
stand in my wayظآز

244
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:47,700
ظآزThis blade will cut through
all worldly judgmentظآز

245
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:52,020
ظآزI am my own kingظآز

246
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,660
ظآزI emerge into the worldظآز

247
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,420
ظآزUnknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial worldظآز

248
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:09,780
ظآزMy pride is my trump cardظآز

249
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:11,580
ظآزEven if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yieldظآز

250
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:12,980
ظآزBorn with a gift, I won't give inظآز

251
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,740
ظآزAgainst heaven's will,
I'll bet on my riseظآز

252
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:16,260
ظآزA sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountainظآز

253
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:17,980
ظآزI dare to break every ruleظآز

254
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:19,300
ظآزI see through
the masks of human heartsظآز

255
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:21,140
ظآزFamous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguiseظآز

256
00:14:21,140 --> 00:14:22,380
ظآزThey kneel and beg for fameظآز

257
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:24,620
ظآزI stand and fight for my dignityظآز

258
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:26,140
ظآزFacing powerful foes, I will not bowظآز

259
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,740
ظآزWith my blade in hand,
I decide what is rightظآز

260
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:29,340
ظآزStand for justice and never step backظآز

261
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:31,060
ظآزEven if the whole world
stands against meظآز

262
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:32,780
ظآزUntamed,
frost has carved me to the boneظآز

263
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:34,140
ظآزOnly then do I become more like myselfظآز

264
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,780
ظآزFight, this life of mine is unyieldingظآز

265
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:37,260
ظآزNo matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through itظآز

266
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:38,980
ظآزFor love, I do not fight for the worldظآز

267
00:14:38,980 --> 00:14:40,580
ظآزI only want
to protect her for a lifetimeظآز

268
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,140
ظآزCarefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stayظآز

269
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:46,460
ظآزNow I know all things can be overcomeظآز

270
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,620
ظآزI raise my blade and change my fateظآز

271
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:51,220
ظآزLet me write the legendظآز

272
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,660
ظآزI rise against fate and fightظآز

273
00:14:58,660 --> 00:15:01,980
ظآزWin or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to meظآز

274
00:15:01,980 --> 00:15:04,460
ظآزEven if I fall, I will still shineظآز

275
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:08,540
ظآزLet my name
be carved into the vast worldظآز

276
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:11,500
ظآزI rise against fate and fightظآز

277
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,980
ظآزIf this world refuses to forgive meظآز

278
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:17,020
ظآزThen I'll burn away
all my edge and brillianceظآز

279
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:22,060
ظآزAnd trade it for a new dawnظآز
